        "created_at": "2016-08-17T10:03:33.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Much to my regret, I\u2019ve never had the '78 Charmes, but it sounds like it actually might be showing more youthfully than the '78 Clos de la Roche. We tasted a couple of bottles of the latter with Jeremy around 13 months ago and his opinion, which I shared, was that now was a good time to drink up.</p>",
